snippet.title: Amber Heard Responds To Johnny Depp In NEW Pirates Of The Caribbean
snippet.description:
Over the last several years, Johnny Depp has been working hard to try and clear his name in all the ways that matter. Not the least of which was that he was accused of being to his now ex-wife of Amber Heard and has been trying to show in court and in the public eye that this was false. The problem though, was that he was getting punished by various people for "failing" to do so, including losing key roles in key films he was meant to be a part. But now, things are changing, and he's very happy about it! We'll break it down for you. Be sure to like the video and subscribe to the channel!

Click HERE To Enter The GIVEAWAY! https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCbiT0LUIbQj6CQScvWHJeKQ?sub_confirmation=1

And there you have it, everyone! A look at everything that has been going on with Johnny Depp and how he is reacting to getting recast as Jack Sparrow and potentially more roles. Are you glad that Johnny Depp is getting his due? Do you think that this will allow him to go and get back other roles or at the very least be considered for them as the charges continue to be proven false? Or, are things going to be murky for him for a while? Let us know in the comments below, be sure to subscribe and we'll see you next time on the channel!
